  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goals of this work will be to 1) develop an ACP educational intervention that will be
      integrated into a standard pre-dialysis program and 2) evaluate its preliminary efficacy on
      increased use of ACP among patients with advanced CKD and their families.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Mixed methods study that will use qualitative methods to develop an ACP educational
      intervention. This intervention will be randomized among patients with advanced chronic
      kidney disease who are referred for pre-dialysis education.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
