  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Stage 4 or 5 CKD (defined by the Modification of Diet in Renal Disease for estimation
             of GFR &lt; 30 ml/min/1.73m2)

          -  Age 65 years or greater

          -  Referred by their primary nephrologist for standard pre-dialysis education

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of dementia

          -  Listed for Kidney Transplantation
      </textblock>
